---
title: Paella Con Huevos with Bell Pepper, Peas, and Smoked Paprika
description: When in doubt, put an egg on it! Add fried eggs to paella, and Spain’s most famous rice dish instantly becomes even more hearty and filling. Not that this one is lacking in ingredients—you’ve also got peas, tomato, bell pepper, and plenty of aromatic spices stirred into those grains. We recommend serving this one straight from the pan so everyone at the table can ooh and ahh over this impressive recipe.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/paella-con-huevos-6dfe3e26.jpg
